    "This transformer-based model offers a computationally lighter alternative to existing models, addressing challenges that arise with the direct application of transformers to image reconstruction tasks.",
    "Unlike traditional transformers, which are adept at handling spatial interactions but struggle with the spatially sparse and spectrally rich nature of hyperspectral images, MST + + innovates by focusing on spectral features.",
    "It introduces Spectral-wise Multi-head Self-Attention (S-MSA), which treats spectral features as tokens to compute self-attention within the spectral domain, bypassing the spatial complexity.",
    "This approach, embodied in the self-attention blocks (SABs) arranged in a U-shaped configuration, allows MST + + to efficiently extract and leverage multi-resolution spectral information, overcoming the inherent computational and spatial challenges of hyperspectral image reconstruction.",
